{"tid":675386,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"雲加：現代球迷冇耐性","createTime":"2018-05-23T12:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-23T14:45:02.000Z","uid":1121,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"08a4220721bb66e621bdc74af195cd561fedf222","tid":675386,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=vpYrFJbs0IQmUCDlfh9O0JnkJiu3DM%2BvEze6mtExKRo%3D&h=3c1a1f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】正當阿仙奴新帥落實，前領隊雲加表示就算贏得歐霸盃冠軍，其結局也不會改變，全因「現代球迷毫無耐性」。<br />\n<br />\n「我同管理層坐在一起商討未來，大家都認同由新領隊接手，對球隊是好事，這樣會讓球迷重新給球會更多時間。」雲加（Arsene Wenger）日前受訪時打開心窗表示：「阿仙奴士氣一流，很榮幸與他們共事，目前陣容的潛力很大，繼任人會有時間追逐冠軍。」<br />\n<br />\n英超收咧，前阿仙奴領隊雲加結束長達22年的領「兵」生涯，由艾美利取代，回想雲加頭10年已贏過3次英超和4次足總盃，惟之後一直與聯賽冠軍無緣，只能增添3座足足總盃冠軍，連續2季失去歐聯資格。<br />\n<br />\n兵工廠一度有機會衝擊歐霸盃冠軍，惜4強被馬體會淘汰出局，雲加補充道：「現在的粉絲不再有耐性，也不再有饒恕，就算之前幾成功，人們也會慢慢習慣。老實說，今季我們殺入聯賽盃決賽，也闖入歐霸盃4強，該獲得更多讚賞，說到尾，就算贏得歐霸盃，我認為人家依然對球隊不再有耐性。」"},{"pid":"b3afb53bbca2bcf8c88fd52466c93870b327506d","tid":675386,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"雲爺爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a68495fb4c1b02aa2fa6751cc2582c8323ec9586","tid":675386,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下椰子就知了"},{"pid":"be82e7bcb3a995fcc66ab50afc22d143147c8cef","tid":675386,"uid":101307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"反雲而家冇曬聲氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛雲加"},{"pid":"b9452bc04f4299f860032f24e81f83030dccb394","tid":675386,"uid":87072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:09:25.000Z","msg":"8年無冠都仲叫冇耐性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30b2cfe33ab3d09f2162d86b07679c4a40518959","tid":675386,"uid":40588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be82e7bcb3a995fcc66ab50afc22d143147c8cef","tid":675386,"uid":101307,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:02:16.000Z","msg":"反雲而家冇曬聲氣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我愛雲加"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:09:59.000Z","msg":"退左休反乜鬼"},{"pid":"a6b202e2fa6a2f84f55062e91a93f61b66ef53d3","tid":675386,"uid":37220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a68495fb4c1b02aa2fa6751cc2582c8323ec9586","tid":675386,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T13:00:16.000Z","msg":"事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇下椰子就知了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-23T14:45:02.000Z","msg":"yes<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}